## Code Review Checklist

Before approving any PR, verify:

- [ ] Types are correct (no `any`, no type assertions without justification)
- [ ] API calls use the standard envelope and handle errors
- [ ] All 4 states rendered (loading, error, empty, data)
- [ ] Business logic has unit tests
- [ ] No `console.log` left in production code
- [ ] No hardcoded strings (use constants or i18n keys)
- [ ] Accessibility basics (keyboard nav, ARIA labels, contrast)
- [ ] Matches the contract spec for this feature
- [ ] No new dependencies without documented rationale

