## PR Template Requirements

Every pull request must include:

```markdown
## What
[1-2 sentence description of the change]

## Why
[Business context or task reference]

## Contract
[Link to the API contract file, or "N/A" for non-API changes]

## Testing
- [ ] Unit tests added/updated
- [ ] Manual testing completed
- [ ] All 4 states verified (if UI change)

## Screenshots
[Before/after if UI change, otherwise "N/A"]
```

